00:00:07.040 --> 00:00:08.629
heart to talk about. I just wanted to

00:00:08.639 --> 00:00:11.270
point out what the Lord did

00:00:11.280 --> 00:00:13.789
whenever we had our prayer time

00:00:13.799 --> 00:00:16.230
yesterday. And you know, I never

00:00:16.240 --> 00:00:18.189
know what he's going to share. It's just

00:00:18.199 --> 00:00:20.630
amazing whenever you start praying and

00:00:20.640 --> 00:00:22.710
the Lord starts revealing things of the

00:00:22.720 --> 00:00:26.070
future to you. Less than 24 hours

00:00:26.080 --> 00:00:29.189
later, Trump announces his mineral

00:00:29.199 --> 00:00:32.389
deal. And I told you all I saw President

00:00:32.389 --> 00:00:32.399
Trump—if

00:00:32.399 --> 00:00:34.870
you watch the prayer time—if

00:00:34.870 --> 00:00:34.880
you are

00:00:34.880 --> 00:00:36.310
skipping out on the

00:00:36.320 --> 00:00:37.830
prayer time just to hear me talk a

00:00:37.840 --> 00:00:39.750
little bit and not praying with us, you

00:00:39.760 --> 00:00:41.910
are missing out. I encourage you to

00:00:41.920 --> 00:00:44.869
listen to the whole video,

00:00:44.879 --> 00:00:46.630
especially if you like to intercede and

00:00:46.640 --> 00:00:49.190
pray for the nations. I believe the Lord

00:00:49.200 --> 00:00:52.150
has called us to this YouTube channel; the

00:00:52.160 --> 00:00:55.029
primary focus is 'Prayer Changes

00:00:55.029 --> 00:00:55.039
Things.'And

00:00:55.039 --> 00:00:57.590
I believe we are changing things in

00:00:57.600 --> 00:00:59.750
nations. Yesterday, I feel like we

00:00:59.760 --> 00:01:01.670
