00:01:27.280 --> 00:01:30.789
and

00:01:30.799 --> 00:01:34.550
a stars and stripes jacket,

00:01:34.560 --> 00:01:36.630
like an American

00:01:36.630 --> 00:01:36.640
flag-looking

00:01:36.640 --> 00:01:40.230
jacket, and he had a top hat on. He

00:01:40.240 --> 00:01:43.190
flew in on a jet plane—it looked like

00:01:43.200 --> 00:01:43.950
an

00:01:43.950 --> 00:01:43.960
