00:01:50.159 --> 00:01:53.350
started negotiating. I

00:01:53.360 --> 00:01:56.230
kept hearing in the spirit realm,

00:01:56.240 --> 00:01:58.469
'The Art of the Deal, the Art of the Deal.'He was

00:01:58.469 --> 00:01:58.479
