00:03:08.400 --> 00:03:10.790
in

00:03:10.800 --> 00:03:14.750
a bundle toward

00:03:14.760 --> 00:03:17.830
France. I could see it pointing

00:03:17.830 --> 00:03:17.840
toward

00:03:17.840 --> 00:03:20.550
France,

00:03:20.560 --> 00:03:22.470
laying down. The

00:03:22.480 --> 00:03:25.110
