00:03:25.120 --> 00:03:28.309
I could see the round

00:03:28.319 --> 00:03:31.470
base of the

00:03:31.470 --> 00:03:31.480
stalks

00:03:31.480 --> 00:03:34.309
of the wheat

00:03:34.319 --> 00:03:36.710
wrapped in a bundle.

00:03:36.720 --> 00:03:39.350
He said,

00:03:39.360 --> 00:03:43.030
'Brandon, this is in play as you

00:03:43.040 --> 00:03:45.910
speak right now. This is about to

00:03:45.910 --> 00:03:45.920
