00:03:45.920 --> 00:03:48.229
could hear it echoing

00:03:48.239 --> 00:03:50.630
inside of me that this major mineral

00:03:50.640 --> 00:03:54.630
deal was about to take place. Lo

00:03:54.640 --> 00:03:58.710
and behold, 24 hours later—after

00:03:58.710 --> 00:03:58.720
